<div id="pf3878" class="pf w55 h236" data-page-no="3878"><div class="pc pc3878 w55 h236"><div class="t m40f xb6 h4e y29ac ff3 fs19 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">LESSON 1 </div><div class="t md25 x91 h35 y2a66 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">December 31 to January 6 </div><div class="t m260 x76 h104 y2131 ff3 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">CHANNELS OF </div><div class="t m446 x78 h104 y1f34 ff3 fs1c fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">COMMUNICATION </div><div class="t m746 xb7 h5 y103b ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">&quot;The word is nigh thee, even in thy </div><div class="t m14b6 xd4 h5 y10f8 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">mouth, and in thy heart: that is, the word </div><div class="t m5f2 xd4 h5 y961 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of faith, which we preach; that if thou </div><div class="t m5d8 xd4 h5 ycd9 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">shalt confess with thy mouth the Lord </div><div class="t m415 xd4 h5 y74c ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Jesus, and shalt believe in thine heart </div><div class="t m7ef xd4 h5 ye35 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that God hath raised him from the dead, </div><div class="t m44b xd4 h5 y10a0 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">thou shalt be saved. For with the heart </div><div class="t m386 xd4 h5 y11f5 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">man believeth unto righteousness; and </div><div class="t m14d5 xd3 h5 ye67 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">with the mouth confession is made unto </div><div class="t mb3f xd4 h5 yde4 ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">salvation.&quot; Rom. 10:8-10. </div><div class="t m671 xb9 h35 yb86 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Let us not limit the concept of communi-</div><div class="t m964 xd3 h35 y101c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cation to words. We communicate in many </div><div class="t m1e7 xd3 h35 y967 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">ways. Communication is an act of the total </div><div class="t m733 xd3 h35 y1732 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">man. Anything to which people can attach </div><div class="t m4f xd3 h35 y89c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">meaning may be, and is, used in communi-</div><div class="t m540 xd3 h35 ycb5 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">cation. The act of communication is </div><div class="t m36d xd3 h35 ye02 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">extremely broad in its scope. &quot;Our words, </div><div class="t m9c0 xd3 h35 y732 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our actions, our deportment, our dress, </div><div class="t m3c1 xd3 h35 yb8c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">everything, should preach. Not only with </div><div class="t m149a xd3 h35 y532 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">our words should we speak to the people, </div><div class="t m7f9 xd3 h35 y15ab ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">but everything pertaining to our person </div><div class="t m1ab xd3 h35 y75a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">should be a sermon to them, that right </div><div class="t m2d2 xd3 h35 yd30 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">impressions may be made upon them.&quot; </div><div class="t mb31 xd3 h35 y9a8 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">—Testimonies, </div><div class="t m5b0 x53 h35 y9a8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Vol. 2, p. 618. </div><div class="t m22f xb9 h35 y107c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Christian has many ways in which </div><div class="t m113b xd3 h35 yf58 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">to communicate. In fact, he and his church  </div><div class="t m92 x2b h35 ycad ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">are books read by others, often secretly </div><div class="t me15 x2b h35 yf3c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and without his knowledge. &quot;No man is </div><div class="t m2eb xaf h35 yee3 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">an iland, intire of it selfe.&quot;—John Donne. </div><div class="t m192c x2b h5 y121e ff3 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">KEY THOUGHTS </div><div class="t md6b x45 h35 yae1 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">1. </div><div class="t m646 x7 h35 y15aa ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Totality of Christian Witness. </div><div class="t m17f x149 h35 y102b ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">All </div><div class="t m6cf x2b h35 y103c ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">that we do or say communicates to </div><div class="t m8a8 x2b h35 y7dd ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">others,— a sobering concept in our task </div><div class="t md4 x2b h35 yed0 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">of warning the world about Jesus&apos; return </div><div class="t mcf6 x1f h35 y515 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and the preparation necessary for it. </div><div class="t m465 x58 h35 y12d8 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">2. </div><div class="t ma13 x86 h35 y118e ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">The Power of Christian Witness. </div><div class="t md2a x1f h35 y72d ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Simple acts of love may have infinite con-</div><div class="t m687 x1f h35 y10a1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">sequence. On the other hand neglect may </div><div class="t m2bb x2b h35 ye13 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">leave us responsible for others&apos; loss. </div><div class="t m47e x58 h35 yc0d ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">3. </div><div class="t m863 xae h35 yce0 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Reflex Action of Christian Witness. </div><div class="t m410 x1f h35 yd15 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">A consciousness of the use the Holy Spirit </div><div class="t m9e4 x1f h35 yf74 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">may make of our acts and words will affect </div><div class="t ma49 x1f h35 yc0e ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">the basic nature of our lives. </div><div class="t m2a4 x7 h35 yd16 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">An article by Ellen G. White, &quot;Ye </div><div class="t m134d xb0 h35 ycb8 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Are the Light of the World,&quot; appears </div><div class="t m9d6 xb0 h35 yabf ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">following this lesson. It was orig-</div><div class="t m154 xb0 h35 y75a ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">inally printed in the </div><div class="t ma44 xdc h35 yd4c ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Review and </div><div class="t m2ef xb0 h35 y3b5 ff5 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">Herald </div><div class="t m4a6 xac h35 ycba ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">and is reprinted here for </div><div class="t m3e2 xb0 h35 y12e1 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">reading in conjunction with this </div><div class="t m1289 xb0 h35 yb94 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">week&apos;s lesson. </div><div class="t m777 x17a h35 y2130 ff2 fs3 fc0 sc0 ls0 ws0">7 </div></div><div class="pi" data-data='{"ctm":[1.000000,0.000000,0.000000,1.000000,0.000000,0.000000]}'></div></div>
